# SERVESAGE Roadmap

This document outlines the development roadmap for SERVESAGE.  
Our focus is on delivering **practical, high-value insights** to service companies from day one.  

---

## ✅ Phase 1 – MVP (Current Development)
- [x] Conversion KPI Tracking (Assessment → Fulfillment)
- [x] Technician Performance Dashboard
- [ ] Exportable PDF/Excel Reports
- [ ] Demo-ready sample dataset

---

## 🔄 Phase 2 – Forecasting & Growth Insights
- [ ] AI-powered demand forecasting (seasonal patterns, staffing needs)
- [ ] Profitability analysis by job type
- [ ] Repeat visit reduction tracking
- [ ] Technician leaderboard (gamified option)

---

## 🚀 Phase 3 – Enterprise Expansion
- [ ] Role-based dashboards (Owner / Ops Manager / Technician views)
- [ ] Multi-location rollups
- [ ] Advanced benchmarking (compare techs, departments, or locations)
- [ ] Integration with CSAT/CX feedback tools

---

## 🌍 Long-Term Vision
- Continuous learning AI engine that adapts to each business’s unique patterns
- Automated coaching recommendations for technicians
- Partner ecosystem for plugins and integrations

---

